title: Undie runs and rub-downs: Warnie’s big day out
text:
THIS time last year, Shane Warne was deep in the African jungle on I’m A Celeb, subsisting on beans and rice and having to make nice with a bunch of B-listers infinitely less famous than he. 
So you’ll forgive him if, a year on, he’s indulging in the fruits of freedom. 
Warne’s Sunday — as captured by ever-present paparazzi snappers — was rather bizarre, even by Warnie standards. It started, snappers tell us, with his daughter Brooke sitting on the footpath outside his Brighton mansion waiting for an Uber to transport her to mother Simone Callahan’s nearby home. 
Moments later Shane made an, ahem, brief appearance outside his house: What do YOU wear when you leave the house — clothes? Picture: Diimex Source: Diimex Warnie got back. Picture: Diimex Source: Diimex Plot twist: THEY’RE NOT EVEN WARNIE-BRAND SPINNERS UNDIES. Picture: Diimex Source: Diimex 
Later in the day, the cricket legend headed to Crown Casino where he was seen receiving a one-on-one massage WHILE PLAYING POKER. Folks, this is next-level baller behaviour: Nothing to see here folks, just a cricket legend gettin’ a rub down. Picture: Diimex Source: Diimex 
Particular attention was paid to the former cricketer’s buttocks, which must’ve been a thrill for the surrounding gamblers: I, too, carry a lot of tension in my butt. Picture: Diimex Source: Diimex Incredible that the weirdest thing in this picture ISN’T the dude wearing sunnies inside. Picture: Diimex Source: Diimex 
Haters gonna hate, but Shane Warne is truly living his best life.
